00:14.284 --> 00:15.852
Now they want to do this at a bar?

00:15.877 --> 00:18.612
What happened to outside?
Somewhere more neutral.

00:18.653 --> 00:20.654
Yeah, man, my connection's
on their side.

00:20.682 --> 00:22.282
But we'll be good.

00:22.317 --> 00:24.918
You cool with this?

00:24.953 --> 00:27.254
Lamar say we good, we good.

00:29.490 --> 00:31.258
You known him a little over three weeks.

00:31.292 --> 00:32.593
And already this your best friend?

00:32.618 --> 00:35.162
Malik, talk a little less,

00:35.196 --> 00:37.097
listen to your brother more.

00:37.131 --> 00:39.266
He's obviously a terrific
judge of character.

00:39.300 --> 00:41.802
Let's get this done.

00:48.076 --> 00:51.044
[rock music playing]

00:51.079 --> 00:57.184
♪

00:57.218 --> 01:00.754
Party's in the back.
Let's keep it moving.

01:01.646 --> 01:03.647
Afternoon.

01:06.469 --> 01:07.979
Got eyes on Atwater.

01:08.004 --> 01:10.776
He's headed towards the back room.

01:12.609 --> 01:15.611
[knock at door, door opening]

01:17.480 --> 01:20.425
How we doin'? What up, Ryan?

01:20.613 --> 01:22.381
- You're late.
- I don't know my way

01:22.415 --> 01:24.383
around Canaryville like that.
You know that, bro.

01:24.417 --> 01:26.385
[scoffs] More like Crackerville.

01:26.419 --> 01:28.453
- Yeah, right.
- What did you say?

01:28.488 --> 01:29.888
Nah, man, Malik just be playin', bro.

01:29.922 --> 01:31.724
You're a funny dude.

01:31.749 --> 01:34.284
Just playin'. [scoffs]

01:34.318 --> 01:36.286
Yeah, bro, and that's
his brother, Shabazz.

01:36.320 --> 01:38.221
He's my dude I told you about.

01:38.255 --> 01:39.789
All right, cool. This is Dexter.

01:39.824 --> 01:42.325
- That's his cousin, Nate.
- What's up, gentlemen?

01:42.359 --> 01:44.127
All right, so where the M4s at?

01:44.161 --> 01:46.830
[chuckling]

01:46.864 --> 01:48.832
Why don't we get a drink, you know?

01:48.866 --> 01:50.533
Play a little nine-ball.

01:50.568 --> 01:52.502
Get to know each other a little better.

01:53.003 --> 01:54.871
We just came to do business.

01:54.905 --> 01:56.406
Not have a tea party.

01:56.440 --> 01:59.008
I like to know who I work with.

01:59.877 --> 02:02.479
What's this?

02:02.513 --> 02:04.013
Yo, what's up, man, trying
to play us like

02:04.048 --> 02:06.483
- a bunch of punks.
- Watch yourself.

02:07.952 --> 02:10.820
Watch myself?

02:10.854 --> 02:12.188
All right, chill, man.

02:12.223 --> 02:13.256
Why don't you make me watch myself?

02:13.290 --> 02:14.691
Yo, Malik, man, chill out.

02:14.725 --> 02:16.192
- Yo, hey, hey, yo!
- Easy, come on, man.

02:16.227 --> 02:17.660
The hell are you doin' man?

02:17.695 --> 02:19.429
Sarge, we got action in the back room.

02:19.463 --> 02:21.898
Just stand down.
No one said the safe word.

02:21.932 --> 02:24.534
Let Atwater and Halstead handle it.

02:25.302 --> 02:26.836
<i>Hell is this, man?</i>

02:26.871 --> 02:28.238
We just came to get these guns

02:28.272 --> 02:29.606
and get out your way.
You wanna put that down?

02:29.640 --> 02:32.041
I'm just showing Malik the merchandise.

02:32.076 --> 02:34.778
M4-A1 carbine, fully automatic.

02:34.812 --> 02:36.246
30 rounds in three seconds.

02:36.280 --> 02:37.781
Hey, come on, man. Cut it out.

02:37.815 --> 02:38.948
Cuts through the side of a tank

02:38.983 --> 02:40.350
like a stick of butter.

02:40.384 --> 02:42.685
Imagine what it would do to your head.

02:42.720 --> 02:45.722
You so tough, pull the trigger.

02:45.756 --> 02:48.725
<i>[tense music]</i>

02:48.759 --> 02:54.297
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:54.331 --> 02:55.865
Look, guys, let's, um...

02:55.900 --> 02:57.901
Let's get that drink, huh?
Let's play some pool.

02:57.935 --> 02:59.903
Come on, man.

02:59.937 --> 03:02.739
We ain't finna play pool
with these punk-ass bitches.

03:02.773 --> 03:03.873
- [grunts]
- [groans]

03:03.908 --> 03:05.208
- Dude!
- Come on, bro,

03:05.242 --> 03:06.643
you know that was uncalled for.

03:06.677 --> 03:08.411
- Who's the bitch now?
- Hey, come on, man...

03:08.445 --> 03:09.913
- Say you're sorry.
- Yo, just leave it!

03:09.947 --> 03:11.080
I want him to say it.

03:11.115 --> 03:13.082
I'm not saying nothin'.

03:15.252 --> 03:17.287
You ain't worth the bullet, bitch.

03:17.321 --> 03:19.255
Come on, let's go. Nah, we out of here.

03:19.290 --> 03:21.090
Let's go, let's go!

03:21.125 --> 03:23.793
Come on! Here we go.

03:27.998 --> 03:29.165
Jay!

03:29.200 --> 03:30.733
What the hell is going on, man?

03:30.768 --> 03:32.302
We came in to make a deal.
What they playin' games for?

03:32.336 --> 03:33.903
Hold up, man!
It was a go on our side, too,

03:33.938 --> 03:35.238
all right? Get your boy in line!

03:35.272 --> 03:36.773
- Really, dawg?
- Hey, wait, your guys

03:36.807 --> 03:38.441
- have the guns, right?
- The gun that Nate pulled

03:38.475 --> 03:40.243
was definitely an M4, that much I know.

03:40.277 --> 03:41.678
I don't know how many
they actually have, though.

03:41.712 --> 03:43.146
All right, so were
these guys being careful,

03:43.180 --> 03:44.747
or were they just trying to buy time

03:44.782 --> 03:46.516
'cause they don't have
the guns in their possession?

03:46.550 --> 03:48.351
It's unclear... Dexter plays
everything close to the vest.

03:48.385 --> 03:50.587
Okay, so let's keep this thing alive.

03:50.621 --> 03:53.256
All right? Jay, Kevin, you stay under.

03:53.290 --> 03:55.458
Try to make this gun deal happen.

03:55.492 --> 03:58.862
'Kay? We have gotta get
these M4s off the street.

03:58.896 --> 04:00.930
They're too powerful.

04:00.965 --> 04:02.632
Let's go.

04:06.203 --> 04:08.838
What the hell do you want?

04:08.873 --> 04:10.306
Hmm?

04:12.877 --> 04:15.778
Bad news, Al.
Grand jury voted to indict.

04:15.813 --> 04:18.014
You're under arrest for
the murder of Kevin Bingham.

04:18.048 --> 04:20.617
Stand up.

04:20.651 --> 04:23.219
We're gonna need your weapon and badge.

04:23.254 --> 04:24.687
What, are you kidding me? Handcuffs?

04:24.722 --> 04:26.289
He's got 30 years on the job.

04:26.323 --> 04:29.826
Weapon. And badge. Now.

04:29.860 --> 04:32.829
<i>[somber music]</i>

04:32.863 --> 04:35.899
<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:35.933 --> 04:38.968
Slowly.

04:39.003 --> 04:46.276
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:06.363 --> 05:08.798
Let's go.

05:12.803 --> 05:14.537
I got this.

05:15.873 --> 05:22.879
<i>♪ ♪</i>

